title: Richard
text: We worked with Tracey and she is excellent. This company is a great company. They have the lowest prices and they are prompt in answering any questions or concerns. I am highly recommending this company. I have bought Espresso Machines dating back to 1997. I am still thrilled that this company is still in business and they thrive on making their customers happy.
